reviewText: Enjoy this show!  Clean compared to many shows out now.
Has to be my all-time favorite TV show, and I watch a lot of TV! My very favorite Bruce Campbell role--I like to imagine that he's the same kind of hero in real life! (But of course he is!)
I love burn notice it's one of the best tv series on television. Any one who hasn't seen it doesn't know what they are missing. It's bad ass.

Yes, it's a great series.

I didn't realize there was profanity that was muted on regular TV. That's my only disappointment.
stumbled on this show in its last year of broadcast.  rarely see reruns on cable so glad to find this bundled set.
Great quick service. No problems with the DVDs. Enjoy the show but never watched it when it was first on. Now we can.
Burn notice is a well written series and has captivated my affection. This set of DVD's has enabled me to get the full story on every character. I would highly recommend it.

Love the show but the last half of first tape stalls and skips or just stops .  Tapes two and three seem just unusable. Tapes four and five are shrink wrapped and may be fine but I an getting tape two from my library. So we shall see.  Other DVDs all work fine.
